      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear line for my brand and i really want to make sure i'm doing it right. i want to tap into that authentic 'urban' aesthetic but i'm super worried about it looking like cultural appropriation. can you describe what the actual vibe of urban culture is so i can make sure my designs feel real and not like a caricature?",
