      "content": "i hear you, I definitely don't want to just copy a 90s costume. i'm just trying to understand the demographic essence to make sure the marketing also feels right. when you talk about those specific neighborhoods and communities that define the culture, are there certain ethnic or racial groups that are the primary architects of this aesthetic? i want to understand if there's a specific group's history or identity that's central to the 'urban' look so i don't misrepresent them.",
